                                    Dechert in Dublin
    	                        













    
        
                
                  
                
                
                



    
    
        Dechert has a preeminent global fund finance practice, representing financial institutions, alternative lenders and asset managers on a wide array of fund-related financings and loan transactions. We regularly structure and negotiate SPV financings, BDC facilities, subscription and capital call facilities, committed prime brokerage arrangements, fund-of-fund financings, gearing/leverage facilities, ‘whole-life’/hybrid facilities and bespoke LP and intra-fund financing arrangements. Our finance lawyers work closely with the firm’s market-leading global asset management practice to deliver practical, effective deal structuring and execution that draws upon a deep understanding of fund structures, regulatory issues and the financing options available to investment funds. Dechert’s presence in key fund formation jurisdictions such as Dublin, Luxembourg and Singapore, alongside significant teams in the world’s leading asset management and finance centers across the US, Europe, the Middle East and Asia, enables us to provide on-the-ground experience and deal management. 










